race.comment: ZELDA BRAGA (8) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Below best last time at Sandown (29.82) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths fifth. Expected to go close. LETIZIA (3) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (22.30) at this track over 390m. Expecting another good run. SPRING WATCH (7) is among the chances again if he runs up to the latest effort. Something for the Multiples: DOONGALLA ROCKET (4)
